title: Votes cast in the 2006 General elections, Michigan  by county, 2006
name: Votes cast in the 2006 General elections, Michigan  by county, 2006
description: The map is based on data from Michigan Secretary of State website that lists the number of votes cast in 2006 General elections for all races by county. Using census figures for 2005 population levels, a new field has been generated that shows the ratio of votes cast in 2006 mid-term elections to total voting age population (18 and over) by county in 2005.  http://miboecfr.nictusa.com/election/results/06GEN/06GENall.html
